OL,7,FA High Court judge has ordered the
OL,8,Fcompany linked to Tory peer Michelle
OL,9,FMone, must repay the government almost
OL,10,F#122 million for breaching a contract
OL,11,Fto supply 25 million surgical gowns
OL,12,Fduring the coronavirus pandemic.
OL,14,FThe Department of Health and Social
OL,15,FCare (DHSC) sued PPE Medpro, saying
OL,16,Fthe company had provided 25 million
OL,17,F"faulty" gowns that were not sterile
OL,18,Fand therefore could not be used.
