OL,5,CPPE
OL,7,FThe company, a consortium led by Lady
OL,8,FMone's husband, businessman Doug
OL,9,FBarrowman, was awarded Government
OL,10,Fcontracts by the former Conservative
OL,11,Fadministration to supply PPE during
OL,12,Fthe pandemic, after she recommended it
OL,13,Fto ministers.
OL,15,FBoth denied wrongdoing and neither
OL,16,Fgave evidence at the trial in June,
OL,17,Fwhile lawyers for the DHSC said they
OL,18,Fwere "not concerned with any profits
OL,19,Fmade by anybody" and that the case was
OL,20,F"simply about compliance."
