OL,7,FThe Government wants to recover the
OL,8,Fcosts of the #121 million contract, as
OL,9,Fwell as the costs of transporting and
OL,10,Fstoring the items, which amounts to
OL,11,Fover #8,500.
OL,13,FMrs Justice Cockerill gave her ruling
OL,14,Fon Wednesday, with a further hearing
OL,15,Fto take place dealing with
OL,16,Fconsequential matters.
OL,18,FAhead of the ruling, PPE Medpro filed
OL,19,Fa "notice of appointment to appoint an
OL,20,Fadministrator" on Tuesday.
