OL,7,FBaroness Mone also accused the
OL,8,Fgovernment of "scapegoating" her and
OL,9,FMr Barrowman in a post on X, in which
OL,10,Fshe claimed that the company had
OL,11,Foffered to settle the case.
OL,13,FShe said: "Doug and I have been
OL,14,Fdeliberately scapegoated and vilified
OL,15,Fin an orchestrated campaign designed
OL,16,Fto distract from catastrophic
OL,17,Fmismanagement of PPE procurement.
