OL,7,F"The government decided to make us the
OL,8,Fposter couple for the PPE scandal, a
OL,9,Fconvenient distraction to take the
OL,10,Fblame off them."
OL,12,FShe continued that instead of settling
OL,13,Fthe case, the DHSC "chose to spend a
OL,14,Fstaggering #5 million of taxpayers'
OL,15,Fmoney pursuing litigation against a
OL,16,Fcompany they knew had no funds."
