OL,7,FIn court documents from May this year,
OL,8,Fthe DHSC said the gowns were delivered
OL,9,Fto the UK in 72 lots between August
OL,10,Fand October 2020, with #121,999,219.20
OL,11,Fpaid to PPE Medpro between July and
OL,12,FAugust that year.
OL,14,FThe department rejected the gowns in
OL,15,FDecember 2020 and told the company it
OL,16,Fwould have to repay the money, but
OL,17,Fthis has not happened, and the gowns
OL,18,Fremain in storage, unable to be used.
