OL,7,FDuring the trial, Paul Stanley KC, for
OL,8,Fthe DHSC, said 99.9999% of the gowns
OL,9,Fshould have been sterile under the
OL,10,Fterms of the contract, equating to one
OL,11,Fin a million being unusable.
OL,13,FThe DHSC claims the contract also
OL,14,Fspecified PPE Medpro had to sterilise
OL,15,Fthe gowns using a "validated process,"
OL,16,Fattested by CE marking, which
OL,17,Findicates a product has met certain
OL,18,Fmedical standards.
