OL,7,FMr Stanley said "none of those things
OL,8,Fhappened," with no validated
OL,9,Fsterilisation process being followed,
OL,10,Fand the gowns supplied with invalid CE
OL,11,Fmarking.
OL,13,FHe also said that 140 gowns were later
OL,14,Ftested for sterility, with 103 failing.
OL,16,FCharles Samek KC, for PPE Medpro, said
OL,17,Fat the close of the trial that the
OL,18,Fgovernment had ordered ten years'
OL,19,Fworth of excess gowns by December 2020
OL,20,Fand that it was suffering from
OL,21,F"buyer's remorse."
