OL,7,FHe said the DHSC approved the gowns
OL,8,Fwithout seeing a valid CE mark and
OL,9,Fthat PPE Medpro "did not pretend" to
OL,10,Fhave one because it did not need it.
OL,12,FAfter delivery, the gowns were kept in
OL,13,Fshipping containers for "at least
OL,14,Fthree months," he added, and that
OL,15,Fcontamination likely occurred "most
OL,16,Fprobably during the subsequent
OL,17,Ftransportation, storage and handling
OL,18,Fof the tested gowns."
